wdi2-NV.MNF.CHEM.ZS.UN.def: Value added in manufacturing is the sum of gross output less the value of intermediate inputs used in production for industries classified in ISIC major division D. Chemicals correspond to ISIC division 24.
wdi2-NV.MNF.CHEM.ZS.UN.name: Chemicals
wdi2-NV.MNF.CHEM.ZS.UN.source: United Nations Industrial Development Organization, International Yearbook of Industrial Statistics.
